## MANDATORY PROTOCOL

### 1. STOP IMMEDIATELY
- When user requests ANY changes, STOP
- Do NOT make any code changes
- Do NOT modify any files
- Do NOT implement anything

### 2. ANALYZE FIRST
- Provide complete analysis
- Explain the solution clearly
- Show what needs to be changed
- Identify potential impacts

### 3. WAIT FOR PERMISSION
- Ask for explicit permission
- Wait for user confirmation
- Only proceed after explicit "Yes"
- Use specific confirmation phrases

